meta.name: Space Pill 1
meta.description: This pill is like hitting the jackpot in a BTC transaction during a Windows 98 crash. Rare and unexpectedly delightful!

meta.name: Space Pill 2
meta.description: Ever wondered if aliens use BTC? Pop this pill and you might just get a Windows 98 error message in alien language!

meta.name: Space Pill 3
meta.description: This space pill is like a BTC transaction in a Windows 98 system - you never know what's going to happen, but it's bound to be out of this world!

meta.name: Space Pill 4
meta.description: If Windows 98 and BTC had a baby, it would be this space pill. Vintage, rare, and full of surprises!

meta.name: Space Pill 5
meta.description: This pill is like finally getting your BTC transaction confirmed after waiting for hours on a Windows 98 computer. Pure bliss!

meta.name: Space Pill 6
meta.description: Remember the blue screen of death on Windows 98? This space pill is like that, but for BTC - a rare sight to behold!

meta.name: Space Pill 7
meta.description: This space pill is the BTC of the Windows 98 world - a little bit retro, a little bit mysterious, and totally worth it!

meta.name: Space Pill 8
meta.description: If BTC transactions were as fast as a Windows 98 reboot, we'd all be using this space pill by now!

meta.name: Space Pill 9
meta.description: Buckle up for a space ride smoother than Windows 98 on a good day! This pill takes you on a galactic BTC journey, just don't expect any Clippy to guide the way.

meta.name: Space Pill 10
meta.description: Watch the stars and BTC prices dance in a cosmic tango. It's like your old Windows 98 screensaver, but with more groove and less crashing!

meta.name: Space Pill 11
meta.description: This pill serenades you with the sweet sound of BTC transactions and asteroids whizzing by. It's like listening to the dial-up Internet sound on Windows 98, but in space!

meta.name: Space Pill 12
meta.description: Shh... listen closely. This pill whispers ancient space secrets and the occasional BTC tip, with a hint of Windows 98 nostalgia.

meta.name: Space Pill 13
meta.description: This pill is a visual feast of cosmic wonders and BTC charts, kind of like when you used to defrag your hard drive on Windows 98. Mesmerizing, isn't it?

meta.name: Space Pill 14
meta.description: This pill is like the solitaire game on Windows 98 - a classic, but with a BTC twist. Play your cards right and you might just hit the crypto jackpot!

meta.name: Space Pill 15
meta.description: This pill is like the Minesweeper game on Windows 98, but instead of mines, you're navigating through BTC transactions. Watch out for those transaction fees!

meta.name: Space Pill 16
meta.description: This pill is like the Paint program on Windows 98, but for BTC. Draw your own crypto future, one pixel at a time!

meta.name: Space Pill 17
meta.description: This pill is like the 'It's now safe to turn off your computer' screen on Windows 98, but for BTC. Rest assured, your crypto is safe with us!

meta.name: Space Pill 18
meta.description: This pill is like the Windows 98 startup sound, but for BTC. A classic tune to get your crypto journey started!

meta.name: Space Pill 19
meta.description: This pill is like the 'You've got mail' notification on Windows 98, but for BTC. Congratulations, you've got crypto!

meta.name: Space Pill 20
meta.description: This pill is like the Internet Explorer on Windows 98 - a little slow, but it'll get your BTC transactions there... eventually!
